title: Number of homicide offences in England and Wales 2002 to 2019
summary: In general Number of homicides offences has stayed the same over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015/16 and 2016/17.
The highest Number of homicides offences, of value 775.0 was reached at Year 2007/08
The lowest Number of homicides offences, of value 533.0 was reported at Year 2013/14
